                <note rend="inline" type="source">814.00/666: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Southgate</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-04-15T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 15, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>10. You are instructed to inform the Government of Guatemala that the President
                    has determined to recognize the Oellana Government as the Government of that
                    Republic. You may, at the same time, express to the Minister for Foreign Affairs
                    the gratification caused this Government by the resumption of the friendly
                    relations which have so long continued between the two Republics.<note n="4"
                        xml:id="d387fn4">This instruction was carried out on Apr. 17 (file no.
                        814.00/682).</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
